title: Seitokai Yakuindomo Vol 13 Ch 410
text: Read Seitokai Yakuindomo Manga Online I applied here since it's a close walk from my house. But it's really full of girls, huh? In this 4-koma series Tsuda Takatoshi is a new student in the recently gender-integrated high school. He's asked to join the student council as the vice president. Thus begins his days as the only normal boy among 3 female student council officers...
